description: Don't miss the opportunity to own this stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in the desirable neighborhood of Maplewood. This well-maintained property features a spacious layout with an updated kitchen, luxurious master suite, and a fenced backyard perfect for family gatherings. The flexible space upstairs can be used as a home office or game room. With easy access to parks, dining, and top-rated schools, this Maplewood gem is the perfect place to call home.
neighborhood_description: Situated close to Downtown, Maplewood offers a unique combination of suburban charm and urban convenience. Enjoy the vibrant Main Street lined with boutique shops, restaurants, and local businesses. Families frequent the numerous parks in the area for outdoor activities and community events. Maplewood's strong sense of community and top-rated school district make it one of the most sought-after neighborhoods in the city.

description: Experience luxurious living in this exquisite 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in the prestigious Pacific Heights neighborhood. This beautifully renovated property features high-end finishes, hardwood floors, and a gourmet kitchen with top-of-the-line appliances. The spacious master suite includes a spa-like bathroom with a soaking tub and a walk-in closet. Enjoy entertaining in the backyard oasis with a deck perfect for al fresco dining. This Pacific Heights gem offers elegant living spaces and modern amenities.
neighborhood_description: Pacific Heights is a renowned neighborhood known for its panoramic views of the city and iconic mansions. Just steps away from bustling cafes, designer boutiques, and acclaimed restaurants on Fillmore Street, Pacific Heights offers the ultimate urban lifestyle. description: Discover this exquisite 4-bedroom 3-bathroom home in the sought-after Willow Creek neighborhood. With a spacious layout, high ceilings, and large windows, this home is filled with natural light and warmth throughout. The gourmet kitchen features granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, perfect for hosting gatherings with family and friends. Step outside to the well-manicured backyard with a built-in BBQ area and luxurious swimming pool, ideal for outdoor entertaining. This Willow Creek gem is the perfect blend of sophistication, comfort, and convenience.
neighborhood_description: Located in the heart of the Willow Creek neighborhood, residents have easy access to top-rated schools, shopping centers, and parks. Get your morning workout in at the Willow Creek Fitness Center or enjoy a playdate at the nearby Willow Creek Park. With excellent dining options nearby and a sense of community, Willow Creek is a perfect place to call home.

description: Don't miss out on this spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in the desirable Sunny Brooke neighborhood. The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining, featuring a gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. The main bedroom suite offers a large walk-in closet and a relaxing en suite bathroom with a luxurious soaking tub. Enjoy the outdoor patio space surrounded by lush landscaping, providing a private oasis for relaxation and dining al fresco.
neighborhood_description: Sunny Brooke is known for its scenic parks, hiking trails, and top-rated schools, making it a prime location for families. The neighborhood boasts tree-lined streets and a sense of privacy while still offering convenient access to shopping centers, dining options, and major highways for easy commuting.

description: Welcome to this spacious family home located in the quiet and peaceful neighborhood of Maplewood Terrace. This beautifully maintained 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom property features a generous living area with a cozy fireplace, a formal dining room, and a fully updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances. The master bedroom offers a walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom, while the backyard includes a patio and lush greenery ideal for outdoor gatherings. Enjoy suburban tranquility and a sense of community in Maplewood Terrace.
neighborhood_description: Maplewood Terrace is known for its top-rated schools, well-kept parks, and family-oriented atmosphere. The neighborhood boasts tree-lined streets for leisurely walks and bicycle rides, with multiple playgrounds and recreational facilities for children and families to enjoy. Conveniently located near shopping centers, dining options, and close freeway access, Maplewood Terrace offers a peaceful suburban lifestyle with easy access to urban amenities.

description: Situated in the prestigious neighborhood of Willowbrook, this stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom property is your dream home come true. The spacious open floor plan includes a gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a cozy breakfast nook. The grand master suite features a luxurious en-suite bathroom with a soaking tub and separate shower. The backyard oasis with a spacious yard and patio is perfect for entertaining. Indulge in the luxurious lifestyle that Willowbrook offers in this elegant home.
neighborhood_description: Willowbrook is a highly sought-after neighborhood known for its upscale homes, top-rated schools, and lush green spaces. Enjoy easy access to shopping destinations, upscale dining options, and premier golf courses. Residents relish in the serene atmosphere and strong sense of community found in Willowbrook, making it a desirable location for families and professionals alike.

description: This beautiful 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is located in the quiet and family-friendly neighborhood of Willow Creek. The updated kitchen features granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, complemented by an adjoining dining area with french doors leading to a spacious backyard. Relax in the cozy living room with a fireplace or retreat to the master bedroom with an en suite bathroom. Enjoy the pristine landscaping and curb appeal of this Willow Creek gem.
neighborhood_description: Willow Creek is a tranquil and scenic neighborhood known for its well-maintained parks, walking trails, and excellent schools. Families will appreciate the sense of community and convenience of nearby shopping centers and recreational facilities. With easy access to major highways and expressways, commuting to downtown or exploring nearby attractions is convenient for Willow Creek residents.

description: Welcome to this spacious and elegantly designed 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in the prestigious Sunnyvale Estates neighborhood. This Mediterranean-style property features an expansive living room with high ceilings and large windows that provide abundant natural light throughout the house. The gourmet kitchen boasts sleek granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The master suite leads to a private balcony overlooking the lush backyard oasis complete with a sparkling pool and entertainment area. Perfect for indoor-outdoor living and hosting gatherings, this home is a true retreat.
neighborhood_description: Sunnyvale Estates is known for its upscale residences, excellent schools, and serene environment. Gated green spaces and manicured parks are abundant in this family-friendly neighborhood, providing the perfect setting for outdoor fun and to enjoy nature's beauty. Alongside its close proximity to luxury shopping centers and fine dining options, Sunnyvale Estates offers a harmonious blend of comfort, style, and upscale living.

description: Immaculately maintained 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in the desirable Hillside Heights neighborhood. This spacious property greets you with a grand entrance and stunning foyer. The open living room with a fireplace is perfect for entertaining guests. The chef's kitchen features granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Relax in the fully fenced backyard oasis with a pool, spa, and lush landscaping. Luxury living awaits in Hillside Heights!
neighborhood_description: Hillside Heights is a family-friendly neighborhood known for its top-rated schools, parks, and tree-lined streets. Enjoy outdoor activities at the nearby Southridge Park or explore the shops and restaurants along Main Street. Conveniently located near commuter routes and public transit options, Hillside Heights offers the perfect blend of suburban charm and urban amenities.

description: Located in the sunny neighborhood of Sunnyvale, this spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers a modern open floor plan with high ceilings and sleek finishes. The gourmet kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and a large island perfect for entertaining. The master suite features a walk-in closet and a luxurious en suite bathroom. The backyard oasis includes a deck and lush landscaping ideal for outdoor relaxation. This bright and airy home is perfect for families looking for a contemporary living space in a desirable area.
neighborhood_description: Sunnyvale is known for its thriving tech community and vibrant culture. Enjoy outdoor activities at the nearby Baylands Park or shops and dining at Murphy Avenue. Conveniently located with easy access to major tech companies and highways, this neighborhood offers the perfect blend of suburban tranquility and urban convenience.
